# Normalize all text files to LF in the repo. This box edits files from both
# Windows and WSL; without this, Windows-side edits introduce CRLF and produce
# whole-file phantom diffs (and broke an in-progress branch checkout once).
# The app builds and deploys on Linux, so LF is the canonical ending.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary files: never touch line endings.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.db binary
